  "prompt": "What happens on teachers day at Vibrant Academy?",
  "response": "On Teachers' Day, Vibrant Academy typically organizes special activities to honor and appreciate the contributions of their teachers. This may include student performances, speeches, and gifts or cards made by students expressing their gratitude. Celebrations often involve fun events, competitions, and opportunities for students to interact with their teachers in a more relaxed setting, highlighting the important role educators play in shaping their futures. If you need specific details about how Vibrant Academy celebrates Teachers' Day this year, it would be best to check their official communications or website.",
